ans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">简历一份。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">身份证原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">③</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">近期正面免冠二寸照片</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">张。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">④</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">毕业证书及学位证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">英语、计算机等级考试合格证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">⑥</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">获奖证书原件及复印件一份</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.65pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>七、</span></b><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">考试</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'background: white; margin: 7.5pt 0cm; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(21, 21, 21); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">考试方式分笔试、技能考核和面试，内容侧重于临床专业知识、基本技能和综合素质测试。社会化学员考试具体时间和地点另行通知，免收考试费。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.65pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>八、</span></b><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">体检及录取</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">根据考试总成绩，从高分到低分按招收人数</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">∶</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">确定体检人员，体检标准参照《国家公务员录用体检通用标准（试行）》。对体检合格录取人员，按照相关规定签订培训协议，办理有关手续。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18.65pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/xls.gif\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2022/05/16/20220516163526443.xls\">个人简历.xls</a>\',\n  ),\n  \'views\' => 9617,\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'model\' => \'article\',\n  \'verified\' => \'1\',\n  \'action\' => \'update\',\n  \'id\' => \'3267\',\n  \'iid\' => \'3267\',\n  \'attachment_hash\' => \'54939e4c49f41d7f\',\n  \'verifier\' => \'宣传处\',\n  \'verified_flag\' => 0,\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n)','1658795957');
INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('6491','0','cms','item','update','3267','864','','宣传处','修改内容(前台) | 盐城市第一人民医院关于招收2022年度 社会化/单位委培住','/index.php/cms/item-list-category-858-page-4','172.16.1.2','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/u.php/cms/item-update?id=3267&model=article&verified=1\',\n  \'cid\' => \'864\',\n  \'title\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院关于招收2022年度 社会化/单位委培住院医师规范化培训学员的公告\',\n  \'title_color\' => \'\',\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'2022-05-16 16:35:28\',\n  \'source\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院\',\n  \'keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'frame\' => \'/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/xls.gif\',\n  \'thumb_width\' => \'328\',\n  \'thumb_height\' => \'247\',\n  \'attribute\' => \n  array (\n    6 => 6,\n  ),\n  \'level_time\' => \'不选则永久有效\',\n  \'level\' => \'\',\n  \'summary\' => \'盐城市第一人民医院创建于1948年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院是国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江苏医\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'verify_frame\' => \'\',\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'content\' => \'<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">盐城市第一人民医院创建于</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1948</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">是国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江苏医药职业学院等十余所高校实习生带教工作</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">并于</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2019</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">医院共设有</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">个院区：主院区、北院区、五官科院区、儿童医院；现有总占地面积</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">20.73</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">万平方米，建筑面积</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">36.64</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">万平方米；固定资产总值近</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">40</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">亿元。建设中的医院二期及医疗综合体工程总建筑面积</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">330000</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">平方米</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">其中研学综合楼将建成容纳</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">600</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">余人的学术报告厅，以及中心实验室、图书馆、临床技能中心、考试中心、现代化学生公寓</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">200</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">余间，床位</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">800</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">余张。全院现有在职职工约</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3500</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，其中博士生导师</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人；硕士生导师</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">66</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人；副教授</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，兼职教授、副教授</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">176</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人；博士</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">96</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，硕士研究生</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">649</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人；另有委培博士</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">70</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，委培硕士</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">36</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，高级职称</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">624</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人。国家、省、市“有突出贡献中青年专家”</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人，省级重点人才</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">70</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人（</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">333</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">、青年人才</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">25</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人；市级重点医学人才</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">45</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">人。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">。医院核定床位</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4100</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">张，目前实际开放床位</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3253</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">张。医院年门诊量近</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">120</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">万人次，出院量约</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">13</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">万人。医院医疗设备先进，现拥有万元以上医疗设备达</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4042</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台（件），大型设备有</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"> PET-CT 1</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台、 核磁共振</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">CT</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">等</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台、带高级</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">CT</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">功能大型</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">DSA4</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台、</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">SPE CT 2</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台、高能直线加速器</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">台等，百万元以上医疗设备达</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">多台件，医疗设备达到国内先进水平。</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">医院重视学科建设，建成了一批特色鲜明的重点专科，其中呼吸内科、骨科、普外科、心内科、检验科、影像科、肿瘤科、神经内科等</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">个科室被评为江苏省临床重点专科；市级临床重点专科</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">34</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">个；检验科等</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">18</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">个科室被评为市医学重点学科。为了更好地选拔优秀人才，培养合格临床医师，我培训基地从即日起面向社会及各单位招收</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">年度住院医师规范化培训社会化</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">单位委培养学员，现将有关事项公告如下：</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">一、基本条件：</span></span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21.25pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">坚持四项基本原则，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">拥护党的路线、方针、政策，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">遵纪守法，品行端正，无违法违纪行为。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21.25pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">高等院校西医医学类相应专业，普通本科以上学历的应、往届毕业生。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21.25pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">身心健康，能胜任住院医师规范化培训的临床学习和工作。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21.25pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">外语要求：原则上具备大学英语四级及以上合格证，报考紧缺专业外语要求可适当放宽。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 21.25pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&ensp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">5.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">计算机水平达到国家或省计算机等级考试一级。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">附加条件</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">年龄要求：原则上本科生不超过</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">周岁，研究生不超过</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">35</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">周岁，紧缺专业年龄适当放宽。</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">单位委培培训学员须出具在职证明及单位委培公函。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">二、</span></b><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">招收专业：</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">全科、内科、外科、外科（神经外科方向）、外科（胸心外科方向）、外科（泌尿外科方向）、外科（整形外科方向）、骨科、眼科、耳鼻喉科、妇产科、神经内科、急诊医学科、重症医学科、儿科、皮肤科、麻醉科、康复医学科、放射科、放射肿瘤科、超声医学科、检验医学科、核医学科、临床病理科，共</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">24</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">个培训专业。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">三、培养年限及要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">医院按照国家卫健委《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》和江苏省卫健委住院医师规范化培训的相关要求，制定培训计划和轮转方案，并严格按照计划对培训学员进行培训。\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">住院医师规范化培训时长根据《住院医师规范化培训的内容与标准（试行）》，结合学员的自身情况，一到三年不等，学员完成培训并通过各项考核者，颁发国家级《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">住培学员在我院培训期间，须履行国家规定的住院医师规范化培训期间应尽的责任和义务，并遵守医院相关管理规定。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">四、盐城市一院住培基地学员的优惠政策：</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">我院于</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院，根据盐城市政府与南京大学合作协议，凡在我院参培的住培学员可择优参加南京大学在职研究生班，结业时通过南京大学在职研究生班各项考核合格可获得“</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">南京大学研究生</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">”学位证。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">我院全科专业基地为盐城市最大的全科培训基地，盐城市全科医学会主任委员、盐城市全科医学研究所均在基地，多次举办省市级学术会议、师资培训、继续教育；为进一步建设全科培训基地，提高教学水平，除增加师资培训，提升基层实践基地水平外，给以全科进一步倾斜支持，包含：提高学员补助、配置导师、专项技能培训等。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">我院招收的社会化学员结业后需自行择业，根据双向选择原则，毕业时考核优秀、紧缺专业的学员同等条件下我院优先录取。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">五、相关规定及待遇</span></b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; color: black; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">委托培训学员在培训期间原人事（劳动）、工资关系不变，委托培训学员的基本工资、基础性绩效及</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">各种社会保险</span><span style=\"background: white; color: black; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">仍由原单位发放，奖励性绩效由我院依据相关管理规定发放：奖励性绩效每人每月基数</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2000</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">元；取得执业医师资格证书后，并在我院注册，每人每月增加发放</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">元。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">2.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">培训学员在培养期间免收培训费，并给予伙食补助</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>360</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">元</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">人，医院免费提供住宿（或给予租房补助</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>300</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">元</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">月</span><span style=\\\'line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'>/</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">人），并根据院内实际情况给予相应的夜班费、</span><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">节假日加班费等补助。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">3.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">所有参加住院医师规范化培训的学员，需遵守我院的相关管理规定，奖励性绩效经考核后</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">发放。对在各种评优及院内外竞赛活动中获奖的学员医院给予一定的物质奖励。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">4.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"background: white; color: black; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">社会化学员基本工资、绩效工资及相关保险发放标准参照我院同等条件住院医师工资水平。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">5.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">委培学员必须为派</span><span style=\"background: white; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">送单位在编职工或与单位签订正式聘用合同的职工，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">委培学员培训结束后，学员均回委托培养单位工作，我院不予留用。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 21.25pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\\\'color: black; line-height: 1.5; font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 12pt;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">6.</span><span style=\\\'font: 7pt/normal \"Times New Roman\"; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;\\\'><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"color: black; line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">社会化培训住院医师培训结束后，学员须自主择业。培养期间可根据个人意愿自行终止培养，但须提前</span><span style=\\\'color: black; li