e-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">符合本项目招标公告资格要求的投标的申请人均可参加该项目投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">三、项目概况</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">-</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">疫情防控指挥中心控制台采购及安装项目</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程地点：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">内</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、工程规模：约</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，提供符合现行有关验收标准的合格产品，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、供货要求：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">15</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">日历天</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">四、标段划分及招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">-</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">疫情防控指挥中心控制台采购及安装项目，具体数量及规格等要求详见工程量清单，招标人保留对上述工程规模进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">五、投标人主要资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标人资质要求：投标申请人必须是在中国境内注册，具有有效的含家具生产或家具销售经营范围的营业执照，有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 23pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月