4pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区生活水泵、空调水泵维保项目。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">服务地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区生活水泵、空调水泵维保项目</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">，具体内容详见招标人要求和工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">质量标准：符合国家及行业合格标准，满足相关规范及实际工作需要。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">中标人维保范围内设备在质保期内发生的所有故障由中标人负责修复，因此产生的相关费用（包含但不限于人工费、材料费等所有费用）均由中标人承担。上述费用由投标人考虑到投标报价中，无须单独列项，招标人不另支付上述费用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.5 </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">合同期限：二年，具体进场日期以招标人通知为准，进场时按照招标人要求进行设备验收、移交。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">招标规模：工程造价约<u><span> 12 </span></u>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24.1pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">投标人具备建设行政主管部门核发的机电工程施工总承包或建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级（含）以上施工资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\'margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: 24pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\",\"serif\"; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;\\\'><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.2.1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size